    {
        "content": "<p>MarinPostma created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/10180#discussion_r1942036600\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Is it generally fine to consider those memory access trusted? It seems to me that, in this specific case, this is fine, but the callee cannot assume that address will indeed be aligned and non-trapping, no?</p>\n</blockquote>",
